<SUBJECT>
<P>
POLITICAL PRISONERS -- JORDAN; HUMAN RIGHTS -- JORDAN; PRISONER RELEASES; 
HUSSEIN (KING OF JORDAN) 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
