Dear Mr. Hershiser: 
</P>
<P>
My Dad and me are having an argument. I say that after winning the World Series 
you said: "I'm going to Disneyland." He says that after winning the World 
Series you said: "I'm going to buy Disneyland." Who's right? 
</P>
<P>
Nathaniel from Hawthorne 
</P>
<P>
Dear Orel: 
</P>
<P>
