<P>
NEWSWIRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Swtizerland's No. 1 sled won a World Cup four-man bobsled race, edging Austria 
I by less than half a second at Cervina, Italy. 
</P>
<P>
Switzerland I, composed of Gustav Weder, Bruno Gerber, Lorenz Schindelholz and 
