<P>
Don Johnson and Melanie Griffith are now planning an April wedding -- if 
Griffith can wait that long. "I wish it was tomorrow," the pregnant Oscar 
nominee told People magazine. "He's wonderful. I believe some relationships are 
fated and ours was probably one of them. I'll always love him. He was my first 
love." 
</P>
