<TEXT>
<P>
Look for lots of coverage of Asia this week, with the networks focusing on 
President Bush's attendance at the funeral of Japanese Emperor Hirohito 
followed by Bush's visit to Beijing and Seoul. The three networks, as well as 
Cable News Network, will each have more than a half-dozen correspondents 
reporting from the area. To be included in the Asian trek are CBS' Dan Rather, 
