<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY DIGEST: LOCAL NEWS IN BRIEF; 
</P>
<P>
EL TORO; 
</P>
<P>
WOMAN'S BODY FOUND NEAR MARINE BASE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The nude body of an unidentified woman was found along Lambert Road near the El 
Toro Marine Corps Air Station on Sunday, authorities said. 
</P>
<P>
Teen-agers discovered the body about 1:30 a.m. on Lambert north of Irvine 
Boulevard, Orange County Sheriff's Lt. Ken Lohrey said. The woman appeared to 
be about 20 years old, Lohrey said. 
</P>
<P>
The cause of death is unknown, and an autopsy is scheduled today. 
</P>
</TEXT>
